'''House for Hunger'''是瑞典音乐家[[艾维奇|艾维奇]]在2011年举行的一次巡回演出，艾维奇将巡演的全部收入捐给了慈善机构“{{le|Feeding America}}”<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/content/avicii-dj-charity-hunger-relief-death-tim-bergling/|title=Swedish DJ Avicii Donated Millions to Hunger Charities Before He Died|website=Global Citizen|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514174402/https://www.globalcitizen.org/en/content/avicii-dj-charity-hunger-relief-death-tim-bergling/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==概述==
House for Hunger巡演在27天内举办了26场演出，为Feeding America筹集了超过100万{{USD}}资金，据估计这将为[[美国|美国]]各地家庭提供800万份餐食<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.borgenmagazine.com/european-dj-avicii-helps-feed-america/|title=European DJ Helps Feed America and Fight Hunger|date=2014-02-28|website=BORGEN|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514174405/https://www.borgenmagazine.com/european-dj-avicii-helps-feed-america/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年，艾维奇在[[格莱美|格莱美]]周的两次演出中再次向{{le|FEED基金会|FEED Projects}}捐款。Feeding America主席兼联合创始人{{le|劳伦·布什|Lauren Bush}}说：“我们很高兴能成为艾维奇和Feeding America努力为Feeding America筹集资金的受益者。艾维奇在激励年轻人和家庭音乐产业参与并给予回报方面真正起到了带头作用。”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://celebritiesdogood.com/2013/02/avicii-ash-pournouri-donate-million-meals-feed-foundation-house-hunger/|title=Avicii And Ash Pournouri Donate Two Million Meals For The Feed Foundation In The Name Of House For Hunger|date=2013-02-05|website=Celebrities Do Good|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-14|archive-date=2017-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171221102918/http://celebritiesdogood.com/2013/02/avicii-ash-pournouri-donate-million-meals-feed-foundation-house-hunger/|dead-url=no}}</ref>据估计，这笔捐款将为非洲最贫困地区的项目提供200万{{USD}}的教育资金<ref name=":0" />。

